# **05  RE evolution by phase**

| **RE version** | **Phase** | **Algorithm** | **Impact on users** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **classfirst_v1** | MVP launch | Rule-based. Cohort priors. MMR variety. Bandit. | Day-0 acceptance > 25% target. Cold-start baseline. |
| **classfirst_v2** | Sprint 6 (within MVP) | + Personal history learning. Weights auto-adjust. | Day-7 acceptance improvement 8–12%. |
| **classfirst_v3** | Phase 1 | + Dish embeddings (Word2Vec). | Cross-cuisine discovery improves. Serendipity +15%. |
| **cluster_v1** | Phase 2 | + Cluster-based cold start. | New user Day-0 acceptance: > 25% → > 35%. |
| **ltr_v1** | Phase 3 | Learning-to-Rank. Breaking change → /v2 API. | Overall acceptance +10–15%. |
| **ml_v1** | Year 2+ | Two-tower + neural ranking + CF (ALS). | Full personalisation at scale. |

# **06  Revenue milestones**

| **Phase** | **Revenue event** | **Target metric** | **Dependency** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **MVP** | ₹0. Build the product. | 500 DAU at Day 90 | Product quality + habit loop |
| **Phase 0.5** | ₹0. Extend the product. | 2,000 MAU | ASO + organic word-of-mouth |
| **Phase 1** | Ads go live (free tier). | ₹8–15/free user/month | Ad network + DAU scale |
| **Phase 1.5** | Paywall: ₹99 + ₹149. | 3–5% conversion → ₹60K–2L MRR | 90-day free period complete |
| **Phase 2** | Subscriptions scale. | ₹4L–12.5L MRR | 5,000+ DAU + affiliate prep |
| **Phase 3** | Affiliate commissions. | ₹12.5L–30L MRR | Partnership agreements |
| **Year 2+** | All streams + B2B. | ₹30L+ MRR | Product-market fit confirmed |

